id":18497,"eps":3,"meta_tags":["日本","OVA","BL","小说改","职场"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1994-12-13","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/45/8c/363948_wpfvI.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/45/8c/363948_wpfvI.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/45/8c/363948_wpfvI.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/45/8c/363948_wpfvI.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/45/8c/363948_wpfvI.jpg"},"summary":"Everybody's favorite prehistoric pals are back! Join Littlefoot, Cera, Spike, Ducky and Petrie in this delightful, all-new, feature-length movie. It's an exciting treat, filled with original songs, brilliant animation, and the beloved dinosaurs from the family classic, The Land Before Time. The enchanting tale continues in the beautiful, peaceful Great Valley where Littlefoot and his plant-eating friends live and play under the watchful eyes of their parents. But when mischievous Cera coaxes the group into the forbidden \"Mysterious Beyond\", they soon find themselves in big trouble! The excitement begins when they encounter two egg-snatching struthiomimuses named Ozzie and Strut, a thundering landslide, a pair of ferocious Sharpteeth, and most amazing of all, a mysterious egg that's just about to hatch! In the course of their surprising adventure, Littlefoot and company learn just how hard it is to be a grown up - and how nice it is to be a kid! - in this captivating story of hope, love and trust.","name":"The Land Before Time II: The Great Valley Adventure","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"小脚板走天涯2"},{"v":"The Land Before Time: The Great Valley Adventure"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1994年12月13日"},{"key":"片长","value":"73分钟"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://www.uphe.com/movies/the-land-before-time-the-great-valley-adventure"},{"key":"制作","value":"Universal Cartoon Studios (现Universal Animation Studios)"},{"key":"导演","value":"Roy Allen Smith"},{"key":"脚本","value":"Dev Ross (screenplay by)、John Loy (screenplay by)、John Ludin (screenplay by)"},{"key":"制片人","value":"Roy Allen Smith"},{"key":"音乐","value":"Michael Tavera"},{"key":"剪辑","value":"Jay Bixsen"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":0,"6":0,"7":0,"8":1,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.5},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":2,"wish":2,"collect":3,"doing":1},"id":363948,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1994-12-09","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/ea/59/106726_J4j84.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/ea/59/106726_J4j84.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/ea/59/106726_J4j84.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/ea/59/106726_J4j84.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/ea/59/106726_J4j84.jpg"},"summary":"「漫画ゴラク」で連載された川辺優と山口正人による極道コミックをOVA化。監督を務めた落合正宗は、60年代より東映アニメーション（当時は東映動画）の作品を中心に活躍してきた古参アニメーターである。\r\n　組長の岸田が病床にある中、岸田組の次期組長の座を狙って若頭の伊能が動く。だが岸田にその意思がないと知った伊能は相手を無残に殺害。もともと岸田が次期組長を任せる気でいた若頭補佐の本郷に、凶行の罪をなすりつける。岸田組の組長に伊能がおさまる一方、組を追われた本郷は独自に本郷組を興す。その頃、本郷の兄貴格である京本が出所した。元より血の気の人一倍多い京本は、伊能の言葉に踊らされて本郷との戦争を始めるが……。\r\n　本作の制作はナックが担当。主人公の本郷を堀秀行、伊能は大塚明夫が演じた。","name":"修羅がゆく","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"发售日","value":"1994-12-09"},{"key":"原作","value":"山口正人"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":1,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":6,"wish":4,"collect":3,"doing":0},"id":106726,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["OVA"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1994-12-07","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/8f/c5/160925_o1NZs.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/8f/c5/160925_o1NZs.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/8f/c5/160925_o1NZs.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8f/c5/160925_o1NZs.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/8f/c5/160925_o1NZs.jpg"},"summary":"　いつものように「んばば踊り」をしていたパプワが、体の不調を訴え突然倒れてしまった。パプワ島はシンタローが来るまで外界の人間が訪れない聖域であった。そのため、いかに強靭なパプワも外界から持ち込まれたウイルスには免疫がなく、それに感染したため生死の境をさ迷うまでに弱ってしまった。原因となったシンタローは、責任を痛感しどんな病も治すと言われる花を求めて島の危険地帯・炎の崖へと向かう。また、パプワに恋するくり子も、願い事を一つだけかなえる“ラッキースター”を持って島を訪れていた。TVシリーズの人気を引き継ぎ、原作のエピソードをOVA化。","name":"南国少年パプワくん 星降る夜に会いましょう","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"发售日","value":"1994年12月7日"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":5,"wish":2,"collect":5,"doing":0},"id":160925,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["OVA"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1994-12-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/4b/5f/626166_TppB3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/4b/5f/626166_TppB3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/4b/5f/626166_TppB3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/4b/5f/626166_TppB3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/4b/5f/626166_TppB3.jpg"},"summary":"　後年には実写映画版『ゲゲゲの鬼太郎』の制作にも携わったアニメーションクリエイターの横須賀令子（よこすかれいこ）による、お化けを題材とした単発のミニアニメ。NHK教育のミニ番組「プチプチアニメ」の中で放送されたもので、横須賀が得意とする筆と墨絵を活かした画面作りが特徴である。子キツネをおどろかせようと虎視眈々とするお化け。だがお化けはいろんなものへと姿を変えてみるものの、いたずらっ子の子キツネにふり...","name":"なんじゃもんじゃおばけ","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Nanja Monja Obake"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1994-12-06"},{"key":"导演","value":"よこすかれいこ